         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" source="#chaniotis2012">
            <p><note>c and d</note>: [---] no one shall have authorization to bury someone in
               the sarcophagus or to remove a body, for whoever does this
               will be impious and cursed and a tomb-robber and will pay in
               addition to this for statues of the emperors 6,000 silver denarii,
               of which one-third shall belong to the vindicator.</p>
